{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_34","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve confirmed there isn’t a generic backend “apply parsed chat action” endpoint yet; the live bridge today is a combination of intent parsing, policy evaluation, frontend auto-apply for safe preview actions, durable UI/context event recording, and hydration replay. I’m going to test that actual path rather than inventing unshipped workflow logic just to satisfy the prompt."}}
